{
  "stem": "17515.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 98.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember there was-- there was not much to do.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We [INAUDIBLE] pick up the grass, where they make bricks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "On a hot, sunny day, and clean the [? alley, ?] you know, things like that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 120,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Just given-- do-- do something, nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 121,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was two [? monsters, ?] I tell you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- like I said, lager-- lageralteste, maybe familiar to you?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was Bruno and Leo.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Bruno was short, captain from a submarine, German submarine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Leo was about 300 or 400 pound, tall, tall man.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Monstruous. ?] Also, I believe captain from submarine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 122,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they hid-- hid behind the [? barrack ?] during the [INAUDIBLE] time, both of them, when they were in the concentration camp, Auschwitz, they let them go from prisoner to be [? masters ?] in the concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were prisoners during the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Those was two [? monsters, ?] Leo and Bruno.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, they kill you, they do anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Even-- even they kill German, their friend.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They torture and [INAUDIBLE] unbelievable people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Even I was struck a couple times by him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then-- and then during the lunchtime, by the-- by the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because he was so powerful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When he struck, with one [INAUDIBLE] people [INAUDIBLE] on the ground.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I-- maybe-- maybe I annoyed him or something, that's why.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the people, the Polish people say, [INAUDIBLE], make sure-- make sure he hits you, [INAUDIBLE] fall down.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then I-- I realized, otherwise he'll hit me about six times, I was so strong.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because usually when he struck someone, the men-- men fly down.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, killing, like you see the baseball, they play, from the handle from a shovel, I think, people been killed.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mostly the kapos.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "These were lageralteste, lageralteste.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "One, like [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Like I say, [LAUGHS] I call him [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
